        "id": 1003190
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-06-28T23:32:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "What\u0027s a named template, and what does the string \"header\" do above?\n\nI guess something like template.Must(template.ParseFiles(\"./header.html\")) wouldn\u0027t work?",
      "parentUuid": "eb3d830a_f13783de",
      "revId": "472dd5a58f77d2319f6af327ef265c0fedbc3386",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": false
